{"tid":468454,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★[HK No IT]九巴疑停用路線膠牌　手寫牌頂替！","createTime":"2017-11-14T11:35:00.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-14T12:45:37.000Z","uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"c356eee7dd4907c2948b3b15e7cb3bffe6ab89a5","tid":468454,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-14T11:35:00.000Z","msg":"巴士車頭、車尾的膠料路線牌買少見少。網上更流傳一個壞消息，九巴昨(13日)起已停用路線及地點膠牌，由公司資產部派員到各總站回收。如遇到「壞牌」情況，會暫時<span style=\"color: red;\">用白紙手寫路線號碼</span>。有網民就拍攝到部分巴士轉用手寫路線牌的相片，可見路線數字難以看清，不少網友認為有關安排會為乘客帶來不便。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20171114/photo/bkn-20171114134750454-1114_00822_001_01b.jpg?20171114182847\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20171114%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20171114134750454-1114_00822_001_01b.jpg%3F20171114182847&h=89e220c2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20171114/bkn-20171114134750454-1114_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20171114%2Fbkn-20171114134750454-1114_00822_001.html&d=S2VsF1gsdwE4WwX7sjruN%2F%2F4Bxi6eTjWtF%2F0WJNXpvw%3D&h=5ce3dd5d\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20171114/bkn-20171114134750454-1114_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"e57b9a4b08bb1a78ba76e30669c83c89299dc0ad","tid":468454,"uid":19454,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-14T11:35:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5f4dd4c9f21ca4e7c0d0a20e4f51f7a9af2d9d88","tid":468454,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-14T11:35:48.000Z","msg":"用白紙手寫路線號碼<br />\n用白紙手寫路線號碼<br />\n用白紙手寫路線號碼